snippet.title: Ertugrul of Ulukayin | Early Access Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
We are delighted to announce that our first title "Ertugrul of Ulukayin" will be available on August 16th, 2024. Here is a first look at the gameplay. 

Enjoy!

Add to wishlist! Be the first to play.
